cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.MA, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with temporal logic specifications and their synthesis for control policies. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with probabilistic systems and their control policies. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with control policies for systems modeled by Markov decision processes. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is relevant as the paper deals with control policies for partially known environments. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is less likely but still relevant as the paper deals with the synthesis of control policies.
